title: Data Analyst
description: We are seeking an experienced Data Analyst to join our growing analytics team. You'll work with large datasets, create visualizations, and drive data-driven decision making. Required: Python, SQL, Tableau. 3+ years experience.
agent_notes: Excellent match - specifically mentions Python and SQL which are core requirements. Salary is at the higher end of the range. Company is well-established in the tech sector.

title: Junior Data Analyst - Financial Services
description: Join our finance team as a Junior Data Analyst. Analyze financial data, create reports for stakeholders, and identify trends. Strong Excel required, Python preferred.
agent_notes: Good fit but salary is low. Financial services experience could be valuable. Role emphasizes reporting which aligns with stated interests.

title: Lead Data Analyst
description: Lead our data analytics function in the healthcare sector. Manage a small team, design analytics solutions, and present insights to C-level executives. 5+ years experience, healthcare domain knowledge beneficial.
agent_notes: Highest salary in the search but requires leadership experience. Healthcare domain is new but could be interesting career pivot. Worth considering if open to management track.
